---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Remoji Privacy Policy">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-28 pb-20 text-slate-200">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400">Last updated: March 14, 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Remoji exists to help your team find your custom Slack emojis. We only collect the minimum data needed to
        provide that service.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">What we collect:</strong> custom emoji names and visual metadata, workspace identifiers,
        and basic usage events related to the <code>/remoji</code> command.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">What we do not access:</strong> message content, channel history, or user DMs.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">How we use data:</strong> to index your emoji library and return relevant
        recommendations inside your workspace.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">Data sharing:</strong> we do not sell or share your data with third parties.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">Contact:</strong> If you have questions or want data removed, email
        <a href="mailto:support@getremoji.com" class="text-emerald-200 hover:text-white transition-colors">support@getremoji.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
